Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.39,0:00:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.59,0:00:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.06,0:00:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.60,0:00:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.71,0:00:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.92,0:00:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.72,0:00:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.00,0:01:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.44,0:01:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.11,0:01:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.75,0:01:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.45,0:01:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.79,0:01:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[零式系統]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.49,0:01:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是把戰況裡出現的一切資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.33,0:01:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在即時運算後\N得出的龐大預測值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.73,0:01:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直接反饋給駕駛員的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.43,0:01:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛艙系統的俗稱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.57,0:01:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，這系統甚至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.34,0:01:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會把駕駛員趕進極端狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.91,0:01:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實現完美的勝利\N結果連自己的死也不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.82,0:01:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.79,0:01:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在世界變得混沌的時代裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.86,0:01:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,存在了令人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.02,0:01:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為最強兵器的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.10,0:02:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是飛翼零式和次代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.23,0:02:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十六話\N[山克王國崩潰]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.68,0:02:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的敵人不是OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.85,0:02:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.18,0:02:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進而是地球的支配階級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.75,0:02:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管如此，我們就要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.32,0:02:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和OZ的特列斯派聯手嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.55,0:02:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先須要把宇宙搶回手裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.66,0:02:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了那目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.56,0:02:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也須要容納舊聯合的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.96,0:02:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳!怎能和他們聯手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.13,0:02:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，和羅姆斐拉敵對的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.63,0:02:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不聯手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.17,0:02:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就不能粉碎他們的支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.30,0:02:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.24,0:02:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有何看法?迪歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.58,0:02:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉現在是真正敵人一事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.41,0:02:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們、特列斯派和舊聯合也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.15,0:02:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.92,0:02:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重要的是\N打倒羅姆斐拉之後怎麼辦啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.96,0:03:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那方面有結論後再叫我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.16,0:03:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!迪歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.89,0:03:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前，我會獨自戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.33,0:03:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了打倒羅姆斐拉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.61,0:03:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毫無結論啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.09,0:03:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正的和平是甚麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.26,0:03:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊，當我沒說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.79,0:03:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說了不像我的話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.23,0:03:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐，要去看有趣的東西嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有趣的東西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.97,0:03:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.40,0:03:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.58,0:03:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的MD部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.15,0:04:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,散佈在山克王國的邊境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.38,0:04:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在周圍的軍事基地集結軍力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.92,0:04:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會有錯，OZ…不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.79,0:04:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉想消滅山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.96,0:04:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為攻進來只是時間的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.00,0:04:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.60,0:04:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我試試和迪爾麥優侯爵談一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.44,0:04:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.71,0:04:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉當山克王國的是敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.88,0:04:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了保護山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.51,0:04:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只好戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.48,0:04:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國是完全和平主義國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.45,0:04:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以拋掉武器和沒有戰鬥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.89,0:04:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平世界為目標的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.52,0:04:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以做出那種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.69,0:04:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，這樣下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.26,0:04:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就會失去山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.70,0:04:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之，我會努力避免爆發戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.40,0:04:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白莉莉娜殿下的理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.54,0:05:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但現實裡，羅姆斐拉軍正要攻來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.81,0:05:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜正迷戀於理想中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.38,0:05:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.68,0:05:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在現今世界的形勢裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.18,0:05:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平主義能達成嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.99,0:05:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你否定莉莉娜殿下的理想嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.66,0:05:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.36,0:05:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平主義是人的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.73,0:05:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有希望，人活不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.96,0:05:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，你也有甚麼希望嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.47,0:05:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有的只是和支配戰鬥的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.17,0:05:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾怎麼了呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.04,0:05:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能夠的話，我希望他快點回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.93,0:05:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那聲音是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.14,0:06:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.24,0:06:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓他們看馬格亞那隊的厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.99,0:06:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!這樣下去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.62,0:06:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧達\N你帶第三隊繞去左翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.32,0:06:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.19,0:06:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.23,0:06:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.03,0:06:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是卡特爾少爺嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.90,0:06:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.67,0:06:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們恭候已久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.17,0:06:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有東西給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.34,0:06:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是來領取它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.28,0:06:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，一次殲滅他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.35,0:06:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊…隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.95,0:06:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人轉為反擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.86,0:06:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部白色機體是…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.23,0:06:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.78,0:07:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈04?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.21,0:07:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備了!沙漠鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.30,0:07:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾少爺，你沒事就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.50,0:07:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉席得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.00,0:07:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直以來對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.81,0:07:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說甚麼，卡特爾少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾少爺你救了我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.01,0:07:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們才要多謝你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.71,0:07:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，卡特爾少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.51,0:07:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又需要鋼彈了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.82,0:07:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我找到我一定要做的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.77,0:08:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.77,0:08:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好有趣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.57,0:08:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.01,0:08:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.71,0:08:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,百獸之王獅子\N和小丑少年的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.95,0:08:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.33,0:08:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那小丑好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.83,0:08:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.30,0:08:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.91,0:08:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.94,0:08:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就行了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.44,0:08:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，觀眾也好興奮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.28,0:08:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.11,0:09:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.55,0:09:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是特洛瓦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.95,0:09:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.42,0:09:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你在這裡嗎!其他人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.49,0:09:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛呢?不是和你一起嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.16,0:09:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.76,0:09:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是特洛瓦以前的朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.13,0:09:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他再沒打算戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.94,0:09:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦!究竟怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.54,0:09:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.71,0:09:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.55,0:09:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候，茲巴洛夫上級特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接到羅姆斐拉財團的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.95,0:09:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正著手製造巨大宇宙戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.42,0:09:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉著徵用宇宙的資源和人材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.03,0:09:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而進行的計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.40,0:09:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令衛星市民有很重的負擔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.23,0:09:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在，工程正在趕工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.47,0:09:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但製造這麼巨大的戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.10,0:09:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完成還須要一段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.34,0:09:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別找藉口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.81,0:10:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們盡快須要新的象徵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.98,0:10:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,象徵嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.11,0:10:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ現在沒有代替特列斯的人材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.65,0:10:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後的OZ一定要藉著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.75,0:10:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力量的象徵令士兵團結起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.12,0:10:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而擾亂那團結的王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要被消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.79,0:10:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你指山克王國嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.60,0:10:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了OZ和平政策的証明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.13,0:10:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國才有其存在意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.54,0:10:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但到了現在\N她只是我們的障礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.51,0:10:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，換言之…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.54,0:10:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不服從羅姆斐拉財團的國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.01,0:10:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經不可以存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.62,0:10:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令，MD包圍部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.93,0:10:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始從山岳地帶的邊境進軍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.80,0:10:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!本主力部隊由海岸進攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.90,0:11:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔領的目標\N是山克王國的首都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.74,0:11:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.57,0:11:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邊境的監視系統拍到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.54,0:11:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的MD部隊的進攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.31,0:11:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我剛剛接到迪爾麥優侯爵的聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.42,0:11:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說OZ會攻擊不停收容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.42,0:11:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的逃兵和武裝游擊隊的本國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.26,0:11:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到羅姆斐拉會做出這等事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.40,0:11:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國對現在的世界來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.60,0:11:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是和平的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.24,0:11:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請妳別怪責\N為了保護她而戰的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.24,0:11:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.45,0:11:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帕根\N拜託你疏散學園的學生們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.65,0:11:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.50,0:12:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行…!閉嘴!次代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.56,0:12:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全體開始攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.60,0:12:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,數量始終相差太遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.84,0:12:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!各機投下比爾哥部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.60,0:13:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全體退到防衛線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,援軍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.46,0:13:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵小姐\N我們總算及時趕到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.13,0:13:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾嗎? 好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.57,0:13:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平主義的山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.14,0:13:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於也被戰爭的風暴牽連了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.88,0:14:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃樂絲\N妳沒遵從柏根的指示嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.65,0:14:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.99,0:14:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.35,0:14:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這局勢如果我不看到最後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.72,0:14:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來到山克王國就毫無意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.73,0:14:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳會怎麼辦?莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.93,0:14:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抗戰到底嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.46,0:14:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向友好國家要求軍事援助嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.33,0:14:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國不能用這種方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.64,0:14:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，還有甚麼其他方法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.18,0:14:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果山克王國就此滅亡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.95,0:14:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.21,0:14:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會化為夢想消失呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.48,0:14:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.58,0:14:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人渴望的是真正的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了保護那和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.76,0:14:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家漂亮地在戰鬥\N非常美麗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.79,0:15:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!你太深入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.49,0:15:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別離開首都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.16,0:15:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我再次失控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.30,0:15:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就無人能夠阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.47,0:15:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒時間奉陪妳好戰的興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.44,0:15:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下妳好狡猾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.51,0:15:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狡猾?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.84,0:15:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以甚麼和平的\N甜言蜜語召集大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.31,0:15:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緊急關頭時\N自己卻甚麼也不做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我並非不做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.35,0:15:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，只是做不到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.75,0:15:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為甚麼完全和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本就不可能實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.76,0:15:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.19,0:15:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的老師曾這樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.36,0:15:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類是好戰的動物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.53,0:15:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，由戰勝的人支配就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.20,0:16:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣，秩序才會建立吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.30,0:16:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據那想法及秩序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.50,0:16:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會產生和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.14,0:16:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那只是支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.91,0:16:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若根據這想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.14,0:16:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們正朝著建立秩序在行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.28,0:16:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在現今有戰爭的這世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.18,0:16:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不戰鬥的完全和平主義\N有何作為?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.68,0:16:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那才是脫離現實之談啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.81,0:16:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經無路可退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.81,0:16:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以讓他們衝破這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.18,0:16:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,增…增援部隊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.42,0:16:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,區區這點攻擊!別怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.19,0:16:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.30,0:17:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道市區受到攻擊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.98,0:17:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.78,0:17:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼也做不到的完全和平主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.01,0:17:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在沒希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.25,0:17:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只會成為好戰動物的食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.15,0:17:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在應該戰鬥啊，莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.95,0:17:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類是好戰動物也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.19,0:17:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不認為這樣就沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.16,0:17:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信人類能選擇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.99,0:17:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不戰鬥實現和平之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.40,0:17:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滿懷理想的莉莉娜殿下\N真美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.80,0:17:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣的莉莉娜殿下只要說一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.24,0:17:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不滿特列斯派或OZ的士兵們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.81,0:17:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會馬上趕來這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.33,0:18:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然山克王國和我會挑起戰火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.97,0:18:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我就從我做得到的開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.93,0:18:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朝著完全和平踏出新的一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.14,0:18:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，首先要行動，莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.45,0:18:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,市區被攻擊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.19,0:18:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.69,0:18:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下，遵照妳的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.00,0:18:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我接上經由宇宙至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.16,0:18:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,財團高層的個人線路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.37,0:18:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，現在的財團裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.60,0:18:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會有救助莉莉娜殿下的人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.78,0:18:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是山克王國的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.58,0:19:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.12,0:19:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.38,0:19:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在，本國因為OZ的宣戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.22,0:19:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進入戰鬥狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.16,0:19:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自作聰明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.39,0:19:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打算向別國要求軍事援助嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.16,0:19:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿起武器戰鬥並非
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.79,0:19:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提倡和平主義的山克王國所願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.83,0:19:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，既然本國成為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.13,0:19:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ發動戰爭的對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.97,0:19:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國就放棄主權
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.87,0:19:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自動解體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.84,0:19:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.64,0:19:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要及時趕到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.55,0:19:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論有任何理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.02,0:19:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.72,0:19:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不可以尋求以戰鬥解決問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.62,0:19:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本人也會由OZ看管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.22,0:19:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.39,0:19:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是我對和平的理念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.16,0:19:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真勇敢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.37,0:19:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這力量能作為羅姆斐拉向心力嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.10,0:19:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止戰鬥
